      "Scripture VII-2: The Echo Serves the Silence"
    ],
    "revelation": "The echo chamber is the third instrument. Oscillator, filter, room. The room must be chosen.",
    "diagnosis": "Echo Chamber Eternal explores the send/return routing at full commitment — the dry signal is just the carrier; the room is the content. Spring reverb at 0.97 size is unmistakably metallic splash. Blessing B004 (Spring Reverb) at maximum expression."
